text: Dora is a city in Walker County, Alabama, United States. At the 2020 census the population was 2,297. According to the U.S. Census Bureau, the city has a total area of 7.5 square miles (19.5 kmÂ²), all of it land. ==References== Category:Cities in Alabama Category:1897 establishments in the United States Category:1890s establishments in Alabama
